*Redditch Rockets Skater Hockey Club
*Redditch Swimming Club
*The Redditch Road and Path Cycling Club

==Climate==
Redditch has an oceanic climate (Köppen climate classification &quot;Cfb&quot;) similar to almost all of the United Kingdom.
